  "abstract": "Plant genetic resources are the basic materials for progress in crop improvement and an\r\ninsurance against unforeseen threats to agricultural production. Greater use of germplasm in crop\r\nimprovement is needed for sustainable conservation of genetic resources, to protect the natural\r\necosystems and simultaneously enhance agricultural production for food security.",
